' ============================================
UC_SCM ..> UC_SCM1 : <<include>>
UC_SCM <.. UC_SCM2 : <<extend>>
UC_SCM <.. UC_SCM3 : <<extend>>
UC_SCM <.. UC_SCM4 : <<extend>>
